name: Lead section
description: A concise summary of the article, never divided into sections

name: Body sections
description: Main content of the article, divided into logical sections

name: References
description: Section listing the sources cited in the article

name: See also
description: Internal links to related English Wikipedia articles

name: Further reading
description: Relevant books, articles, or other publications not used as sources

name: External links
description: Relevant and appropriate websites not used as sources

name: Categories
description: Navigational boxes and categories at the end of the article

name: Notes
description: Additional information and explanations not part of the main text
